42 (e) Before the department may approve curricular material for
2026 IN 1004—LS 6983/DI 110

30
1 inclusion on the list under subsection (a), the publisher of the
2 curricular material must:
3 (1) provide the department a written, exact, and standard
4 statewide price for each curricular material; and
