16 subdivisions (1) through (5) and (8) through (10), who serves
17 a two (2) year term.
18 (7) A parent of a student who does not have a disability,
19 nominated by a member described in subdivisions (2), (3), and
20 (5) and approved by a majority of the members described in
21 subdivisions (1) through (5) and (8) through (10), who serves
22 a two (2) year term.
23 (8) One (1) state accredited nonpublic school administrator
