39 the judicial work of the courts in Indiana. All justices of the
40 supreme court, judges of the court of appeals, judges of all trial
41 courts, and any city or town courts, whether having general or
42 special jurisdiction, court clerks, court reporters, and other
2026 IN 1004—LS 6983/DI 110

158
1 officers and employees of the courts shall, upon notice by the
